@node Introduction

@{b}Introduction
------------@{ub}

  AtoZ is a utility to transfer files between the Amiga and the 
Cambridge Z88 portable computer via an RS232 serial link. It currently 
uses the Z88's inbuilt "imp-export" protocol, although others may be
implemented in the future.

@{"Back to top" link Main}

@endnode


